<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Independent Spirit Award nominee Elizabeth Olsen went grocery shopping at Whole Foods in her native Sherman Oaks on Thursday alongside her fiancé, Milo Greene singer Robbie Arnett.</p>

<p>The 31-year-old actress and the 28-year-old musician - both rocking Birkenstock-style sandals - stocked up on food as well as a case of Mountain Valley spring water.</p>

<p>Elizabeth made sure to protect herself and others from the coronavirus by wearing a cloth mask, which California Governor Gavin Newsom made mandatory for all public outings on June 18.  </p>

