<p>As of Thursday, there have been over 244K confirmed COVID-19 cases in Los Angeles County, which has lead to 5,888 deaths - according to Johns Hopkins University.</p>

<p>Last month, Olsen spoke at length of the garden she, Arnett, and their landscape designer Heather Trilling planted in their backyard.</p>

<p>'The garden reminded me there was always something to look forward to even in the smallest moments,' the Sorry for Your Loss producer-star told THR magazine. </p>

